high_descs: Turn around and walk to the freezer.
Open the freezer door, pick up the cup on the top rack, close the freezer door.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Place the cup in the sink, turn the faucet on to partially fill the sink with water, turn the faucet off, wash the cup, drain the sink, pick the cup up.
Turn around and walk toward the stove, look up at the cupboard above the stove.
Open the door of the right cupboard, place the cup in the cupboard, close the door.
anns.task_desc: Get a cup from the freezer, wash it, put it in the cupboard

high_descs: Turn around the walk to the fridge.
Pick up a black cup out of the freezer.
Turn around to walk to the sink.
Wash the cup in the sink, filling it with water.
Turn left to face the cabinets above the stove.
Put the cup with water in the rightmost cabinet above the stove.
anns.task_desc: Fill a cup from the freezer with water to put away in a cabinet.

high_descs: Walk to the fridge on your right.
Grab a glass from the fridge.
Walk to the kitchen sink behind you.
Put the glass in the sink, fill it with water, then grab it.
Go to the kitchen cabinets on your left.
Place the glass of water in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Make a glass of water and put it away.
